title: Regional Focus: Gippsland
abstract: Gippsland gems from the collection of the NFSA.
description: From the outskirts of Melbourne to the breakers of Mallacoota and everything in between, Gippsland takes in a great swathe of our great state. In this package of films from the collection of the National Film and Sound Archive, we've brought together a collection of Gippsland gems – from a pioneering Wilsons Promontory camping trip, to a bustling beet sugar factory, to the romance of the Gippsland Lakes and beyond – sit back and be transported east to 'Victoria's Riviera', with a couple of stops along the way.
